        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "With an aerodynamic cutting edge and a curved handle, this *+2 striking battle axe* is perfectly suited to whirling motions, and in fact seems like it wants to whirl free from your grip. A Strike with this axe that benefits from the sweep trait's circumstance bonus on attack rolls also gains a +2 circumstance bonus to the damage roll.",
